        <item>
          <title>Scherzer allows 2 HRs, leaves Blue Jays debut after 3 innings because of right lat soreness</title>
          <description><![CDATA[TORONTO (AP) — Three-time Cy Young Award winner Max Scherzer left his debut start with the Blue Jays on Saturday because of soreness in his right lat muscle. “I just didn’t feel like I could really let the ball go,” Scherzer said, adding that he felt the soreness during his pregame warmup.]]></description>
          <guid>https://majordigest.com/sports/2025/03/29/scherzer-allows-2-hrs-leaves-blue-jays-debut-after-3-innings-because-of-right-lat-soreness/</guid>
